        <h2>What is CBD?</h2>
        <p>CBD (cannabidiol) is one of more than 113 active compounds found in the hemp plant called cannabinoids. It works to naturally reduce anxiety, pain, and sleep issues without any mind altering effects or "high" for the person using it.</p>
    </div>
