        <h2>The Best Approach</h2>
        <p class="light-6">Spectrum or whole plant–CBD is so called because it contains all forms of cannabinoid available in the plant, whereas Isolate CBD only contains Cannabidiol.</p>
        <p class="light-6">Due to what’s known as the “entourage effect,” full spectrum CBD is considered to be much more effective.</p>
